    "title": "Hiring Hotel Manager at Hilton India South Asia Partners",
    "description": "Join the Hilton India South Asia Partners family as a Hotel Manager in Allahabad. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Hilton India South Asia Partners:\nHilton India South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Flexible working hours\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Allahabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Hilton India South Asia Partners!",
